"https://api.github.com/repos/kymatio/kymatio/milestones/6/labels","id":4908848,"node_id":"MDk6TWlsZXN0b25lNDkwODg0OA==","number":6,"title":"0.3.alpha","description":"","creator":{"login":"lostanlen","id":3943142,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM5NDMxNDI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3943142?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen","html_url":"https://github.com/lostanlen","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"open_issues":13,"closed_issues":30,"state":"open","created_at":"2019-12-06T12:39:56Z","updated_at":"2022-07-06T15:35:01Z","due_on":null,"closed_at":null},"comments":4,"created_at":"2022-06-20T13:03:09Z","updated_at":"2022-06-24T21:51:28Z","closed_at":"2022-06-24T21:51:27Z","author_association":"COLLABORATOR","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"Spotted while reviewing #871 with @janden\r\n\r\nRight now, `out_type='dict'`behaves strangely. \r\n\r\n```python\r\nJ, Q = 2, 1\r\nlength = 1024\r\nS = Scattering1D(J, shape, Q)\r\nx = torch.zeros((5, 10,) + shape)\r\n\r\nSx = S(x)\r\nprint(Sx.shape)\r\n\r\nS.out_type = \"dict\"\r\nSx = S(x)\r\nprint(list(map(lambda v: v.shape, Sx.values())))\r\n```\r\n\r\nResult: \r\n```\r\ntorch.Size([5, 10, 4, 256])\r\n\r\n[torch.Size([5, 10, 1, 256]),\r\n torch.Size([5, 10, 1, 256]),\r\n torch.Size([5, 10, 1, 256]),\r\n torch.Size([5, 10, 1, 256])]\r\n```\r\n\r\nIn other words, `out_type=\"dict\"` is inserting a singleton dimension in penultimate position. This penultimate position serves to concatenate coefficients under `out_type=\"array\"` (it becomes `4` in the example above).\r\n\r\nI am in favor of removing this extra singleton dimension, and making values in `out_type=\"dict\"` more like `'coef'`'s of `out_type=\"list\"`. Compare with \r\n\r\n```python\r\nS.out_type = \"list\"\r\nSx = S(x)\r\nlist(map(lambda v: v['coef'].shape, Sx))\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nResult:\r\n\r\n```\r\n[torch.Size([5, 10, 256]),\r\n torch.Size([5, 10, 256]),\r\n torch.Size([5, 10, 256]),\r\n torch.Size([5, 10, 256])]\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis would be a breaking change, which is why i didn't make it single-handedly in my open PR #871.\r\nI'm curious to hear everyone's thought here? bug or feature?","closed_by":{"login":"lostanlen","id":3943142,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM5NDMxNDI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3943142?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen","html_url":"https://github.com/lostanlen","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lostanlen/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/kymatio/kymatio/issues/895/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/kymatio/kymatio/issues